                     <interp inst="t18310217-202-person1922" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a Police-constable. The prisoner was given to my charge - I took a coat and a shirt off his person.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I know nothing of Challis' coat- this coat and shirt Kitchener lent me.</p>
